name: Rainy Night in Charoen Krung
description:
The good old Asiatique Sky carousel & ferris wheel under a rainy night in Charoen Krung, Bangkok.  

A transformative take on a night photo by Indro Muktiono. The original photo might be included as a part of a future photo collection.

2160 × 2886 seamlessly looping cinemagraph in MP4 format.
